Official gosy.io (previously known golinker) chrome extension

Elevate your browsing experience with Gosy, the ultimate shortcut creator for your favorite links! With Gosy, you can effortlessly create team only or global link shorcuts  to quickly access your most visited websites, web applications, and internal tools.

Key Features:

Effortless Shortcut Creation: Seamlessly generate short links directly from your browser with just a few clicks. Say goodbye to cumbersome URLs and hello to intuitive shortcuts!
Just hit `Cmd + Shift + L` and your short link is ready in your clipboard

Instant Access: Access your links instantly from anywhere in the browser. 

Personalized Experience: Customize your short links to suit your preferences and organizational needs. Organize short links into categories for easy navigation and collaboration with team members.

Cross-Platform Sync: Access your short links across multiple devices and platforms. Gosy syncs seamlessly with your Gosy account, ensuring your shortcuts are always at your fingertips.

Enhanced Productivity: Streamline your workflow and boost productivity with quick access to frequently visited websites and web applications. Spend less time navigating complex URLs and more time getting things done.

Get Started:

Install Gosy today and revolutionize the way you browse the web! Create your free account to unlock advanced features and take control of your browsing experience.
